## 🧪 Want to Build From Source?

Clone the repo and run:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/bitboyb/Slamhaus
cd Slamhaus
make
```

Requires C++17 and `make`. See full setup in the [README on GitHub →](https://github.com/bitboyb/Slamhaus#readme)

